nodes.text: Rybettian Shac was a Rybettian delicacy favored by Moruth Doole. The cooking droid XDL-67 once opined that giving away a keon that cost Captain Ramsey Lanclo 1,500 credits to Imperial Customs agent Hewat was preferable to mining glitterstim and being forced to cook Rybettian Shac for Doole.
